rComments: Such a sweet professor. Really loves to teach and has a lot of knowledge.

Nora was great.  She was fun and funny and a great teacher.  Her knowledge of the subject was amazing and she could answer any question you had.  She was also very patient.  Attendance is mandatory but unless you are lazy that's fine.  She also grades fairly.
Awesome professor, she knows the material very well. If you show up to class and pay attention and participate you should get an A. 2 Papers, 2 exams.
